sequenceDiagram
    participant M as RocketMQ
    participant C as 超时取消消费者
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant Pay as 支付消费者

    M->>C: CANCEL_ORDER_IF_UNPAID
    C->>P: BEGIN
    C->>P: INSERT Inbox
    C->>P: 条件 UPDATE orders

    alt 订单仍为 CREATED/PAYING 且已过期
        P-->>C: affected rows=1
        C->>P: 写取消流水与库存释放 Outbox
        C->>P: COMMIT
        C->>M: ACK
    else 订单已经 PAID
        P-->>C: affected rows=0
        C->>P: 记录幂等无操作
        C->>P: COMMIT
        C->>M: ACK
    end

    Pay->>P: 支付状态也通过条件 UPDATE 竞争
